latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy birthday mumma❤️ @dimple.shah20
latestIgtvVideos.caption: // you really thought all the surprises were over? Hahaha nope. Here’s the last one, I know you’re going to love this and you had not seen this coming at all. There’s so much I want to write but you know what you mean to me so I don’t need to write that down🥰 But THANKYOU FOR BEING MY BEST FRIEND. Thankyou for always believing in me, always teaching me the right things, telling me what I need to hear and not what I want to hear and more than anything teaching me to be a good human being🥺💖 I really don’t know what I’d do if it wasn’t for you, having my back every time I take up something new. Thankyou for being someone who I look up to everyday and teaching me how to stay grounded💛 I love you so so so so so much maa. I hope I could make your day special! LOVE YOU THE MOST HAPPY BIRTHDAYYYY💫💃🏻🤗

latestPosts.caption:
Let the Diwali content begin but with a twist🪔// did not see this coming, did you? I told you guys that what I was posting today was something super special to me & something you’ve seen a lot on my page! OFCOURSE, it was a sitcom reel🤌🏻 got this idea when I was watching one of the thanksgiving episode of friends and Monica said, “we have to start having fun in 15 minutes!!!” & then I thought what would it be like if Monica ever hosts a Diwali party. Then I picked a few of my favourite characters and voila here you have this video❤️ 

Every little detail in this video was thought through for days!!! From outfits to dialogues to the hairstyles to the direction, it was such an elaborate process- but so so so worth it🥹

Ps: all the outfits are just my version of all the characters, from understanding their styles👏🏻

Outfit details:
Monica Geller/ Outfit 1: Custom Made
Alexis Rose/ Outfit 2: @izzumimehta 
Robin Scherbatsky/ Outfit 3: @ruhrindia 
Ruby Matthews/ Outfit 4: @shopaffroz 

All the jewellery by @sonikanjianandji 

Thankyou for helping me with the prettiest & most accurate outfits & accessories✨

Lastly OFCOURSE the team who I could’ve never done this without:
📹(videography): @shotbypayal @payalbhayani 
💇🏻‍♀️(hair): @makeupdiarybyrk
